ukeyboard (2.2-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Automatically select first/restore keyboard layout after activation/deactivation
    of keyboard layout from ukbdcreator.
  * Changed language code of template keyboard layout from en_US to en_XX
    to not conflict with present "English (USA)" layout.
  * Added "Help" menu item to ukbdcreator to display howto.txt.
  * "New" menu item will automatically load template layout.
  * Cleanup of ukbdcreator main menu and toolbar.
  * Fixed broken installation of ukbdcreator. Documentation and template moved
    to /usr/share/ukbdcreator directory (Bug 9323: ukbdcreator 2.2-2 fails to install).

 -- Roman Moravcik <roman.moravcik@gmail.com>  Mon,  1 Mar 2010 12:51:43 +0100

