ukeyboard (2.1-0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added XSBC-Bugtracker field to debian/control.
  * Updated xkb includes in ukeyboard hardware keyboard layouts to use
    data from xkb-data package insted from obsolete xkbdata package
    (due to these old includes, modifier keys were not working on real device).
  * ukeyobard creator UI ported to Maemo5 (Fremantle).
  * Czech dictionary was not visible in Control pannel applet.
  * Fixed switching between Arabic and English layouts (Bug 6980,
    Bugs In The Arabic Hardware Keyboard).
  * Czech and Slovak scv QWERTY keyboard layouts were not working due to the
    inconsistency between layout names.
  * Added Bulgarian (ported from ukeyboard v1.9), Dvorak (by Jaroslav Poriz)
    and Greek (ported from ukeyboard v1.9) hardware keyboard layouts.

